### 1. Create Regular User (Run once)
POST http://localhost:3003/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "john",
  "name": "John Doe",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Create Admin User (Run once)
### Note: If "admin" already exists, this will return the 400 error.
POST http://localhost:3003/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "name": "Admin User",
  "password": "admin123",
  "role": "admin"
}

